        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">
            <strong>🇪🇺 Europe’s largest pension fund dumps Tesla</strong>
          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">Stichting Pensioenfonds ABP <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-13-01-2025-wn2-4-sold-its-585-million-stake" target="_blank">sold its $585 million stake</a> in Tesla over disagreements with Elon Musk’s pay package and concerns over working conditions. The Dutch fund had previously voted against Musk’s record-setting $56 billion stock options deal. Musk’s pay package has also faced legal challenges despite shareholder support. The move highlights growing scrutiny of executive compensation as investors weigh ESG factors in their portfolios.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="0px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
