        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4;"><span style="font-size:20px; padding-right:5px;">→</span><strong>Pound traders brace for steep decline:</strong> The pound could tumble another 8%. Traders have been <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-13-01-2025-m5-10-hedging-below-1.12" target="_blank">hedging below $1.12</a> amid UK fiscal woes and high inflation. Last week’s UK market rout saw bond yields spike and FTSE 250 plummet. Sterling faces pressure as the Bank of England delays rate cuts and investors grow wary of Donald Trump’s economic policies.</p>
