        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4"><span style="font-size:20px; padding-right:5px;">→</span><strong>US regulator proposes stricter crypto protections:</strong> The Consumer Financial Protection Bureau plans to <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-13-01-2025-m7-12-enforce-stricter-rules" target="_blank">enforce stricter rules</a> for digital wallets, holding crypto firms accountable for refunding customers in hacks. This move aligns crypto account protections with those of bank accounts. Proposed changes include applying the Electronic Fund Transfer Act to crypto assets like stablecoins.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
